comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Johnson (PHX) during rebounding that does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) along the sideline.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Bledsoe's (MIL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Brogdon (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Johnson (PHX) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) engages with Ayton (PHX) after the shot is released, but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Ayton (PHX) initiates body/arm contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) after his gather and affects his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) fails to release the free throw attempt within ten seconds of receiving the ball.
Lopez (MIL) makes incidental contact with Booker (PHX) during the rebound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Oubre Jr. (PHX) enters the arc prior to the release of the free throw.

Lopez (MIL) rests his left forearm against Johnson's (PHX) front after his gather and makes marginal contact. Lopez then makes incidental "high-five" contact with Johnson after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Brogdon (MIL) makes marginal contact with Johnson's (PHX) backside after his gather.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps vertically and absorbs the body contact made with Ayton (PHX) during his shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) path and does not deliver the contact.

MOB shows Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Lopez (MIL) along the sideline.  The ball goes out of bounds and after communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Suns ball is confirmed.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) prior to stripping him of the ball during the inbound.
RLS shows Middleton (MIL) and Oubre Jr. (PHX) engage and disengage without affecting the other's ability to freely move during the inbound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits the take foul on Bridges (PHX).
Bledsoe (MIL) engages with Johnson (PHX) along the baseline during the inbound, but the contact made to his arm is marginal and does not affect his FOM.
LLS shows Oubre Jr. (PHX) jumps into Bledsoe's (MIL) path and creates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) commits the take foul on Ayton (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits the take foul on Oubre Jr. (PHX).
[Observable in enhanced video] Oubre Jr. (PHX) crosses the free throw line prior to when the ball enters the cylinder.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits the take foul on Oubre Jr. (PHX).
